{
  "stem": "1975.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we found-- I found some people coming out from one of the bunkers when we came back.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, it was-- we were amazed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We didn't know how they survived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then I found some photos, family photos, which I had in the hiding place, where we used to hide my cousin.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was really-- I mean, this meeting, the Russian soldiers, it was such a feeling that it was beyond explanation.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It's like you see angels coming down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We actually kissed the ground when we saw them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it was-- it was great.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Of course, I-- subsequently, I joined the Russian army, but I will give you more-- explain to you in more detail--",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After I was in Kovno, I-- there was-- they had a draft for-- they drafted all the people at my age approximately.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was medical supervision, and there were many Jews who were actually in charge of that now, because most of the doctors were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my destiny was to go the army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So rather than to be drafted, there was a lieutenant by the name of Gusev, who came to see us, especially those people who spoke Russian, Lithuanian, and German.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he kind of liked me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the fact I had my diploma from the-- which I also saved from the gymnasium, which I folded down to-- and I had that with me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said to me that he was going to talk with his-- with his immediate superior to take me into this special unit, which I became part of.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
